private MethodOutcome processOptionalParam(PreferReturnEnum preferReturn, IUpdateExecutable updateExecutable) {     if (preferReturn != null) {         return updateExecutable.prefer(preferReturn).execute().     }     return updateExecutable.execute(). }

private IUpdateExecutable withOptionalId(IIdType id, IUpdateTyped updateTyped) {     if (ObjectHelper.isNotEmpty(id)) {         return updateTyped.withId(id).     } else {         return updateTyped.     } }

private IUpdateExecutable withOptionalId(String stringId, IUpdateTyped updateTyped) {     if (ObjectHelper.isNotEmpty(stringId)) {         return updateTyped.withId(stringId).     } else {         return updateTyped.     } }
